y 連interview 機會都冇就 show unsuccessful..<br />\n直接被reject 左 拎credit 都唔肯給面試機會..<br />\n<br />\n冇辦法之下去左返工 做assistant engineer 做左2年左右  儲夠$ 之後resign 份工 再去報 non jupas <br />\n<br />\n原本打算去本報 Ive shape Non local U 的Top up degree<br />\n但係上個月lobby 信箱收到 大學的 admissions interview arrangement <br />\n負負碌碌咁就考入左😔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講下做assistant engineer  發生咩事<br />\nBSE 你地都知係風火水電    當初我Ive graduate 之後已為BSE 好撚勁 大把世界      <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">IVE 仔屌打八大</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6a9f98896bdd6a6bf1332e4cc206e10f59475102","tid":318983,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:41:25.000Z","msg":"我入左一間 Engineering 畫CAD AND BIM<br />\n<br />\n但發覺由朝9 晚6 之後到 朝9 晚 8.....<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入職初期人工12k [</span>img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/193654_576abb1d560d626c4fa29734aa96a99c.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F193654_576abb1d560d626c4fa29734aa96a99c.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=BQoWquJAM8OzImBuufav%2FJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=34112ac9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/193654_576abb1d560d626c4fa29734aa96a99c.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n日日被人屌老母  已經系基本<br />\n而且 OT 冇水補<br />\n星期六都要返 朝9 晚 5 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做左一年BSE AE 仔 都係畫CSD 同E&amp;M 圖 同埋被人屌 做狗</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/194010_ece33b536909444dc5291d88a00a8b6a.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F194010_ece33b536909444dc5291d88a00a8b6a.PNG&h=f2cc8ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/194037_523cf881cb369ff422dfb275296b0d43.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F194037_523cf881cb369ff422dfb275296b0d43.PNG&h=cd5a53da&s={S